# Josh Habka Media Information
-----
  
I create blog posts, Youtube videos, podcast episodes, and short-form video content(for platforms like Instagram and Tiktok) on a specific topic so people can learn about it in a way that works best for them. While I have just started on other platforms, my main platforms are Instagram and my Blog. I have around 41K followers on Instagram and around 1K people on my blog email list. I have experience working and partnering with other companies and brands, such as Astrochain and SpaceMatics.  
  
Besides learning and creating educational astronomy content, I do a few other smaller things, giving me a lot of leadership and research experience across different fields. I have worked on a height-adjustable water fountain that received funding from a local municipality, worked with clients on Fiverr on social media growth and computer-related tasks, and more.  
  
I have plans on doing analog astronaut training and missions in 2024 and research opportunities over the summer where I can perform applied research in my passions. I am always open to research opportunities and missions with others.
